* Fixture: ApplianceConfig

| set | Free50 | acctfree50%%start_time%% |
| set | Standard | acctstandard%%start_time%% |
| set | Comped | acctcomped%%start_time%% |
| set | Paid | acctpaid%%start_time%% |
